'''Jalalzai''' (or '''Jalaazayi''') is a [[Pashtun tribe]] settled in [[Khyber_Pakhtunkhwa#Southern_Khyber_Pakhtunkhwa|Southern Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]] and [[Afghanistan]]. {{citation needed|date=October 2017}}
==Sub branches==
Main sub branches of Jalalzai include Merozai, Karimzai, Kamaludinzai, Shabozai, Shahizai, Mehmanzai, Khwajezai, Babakarzai, Khudizai, Talkhanzai, and Jogezai.

