The '''murasu''' ([[Tamil language|Tamil]]: முரசு) is an ancient [[percussion]] instrument used in the state of [[Tamil Nadu]], [[India]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://siragu.com/?p=8036|title=மனித நோய் தீர்க்கும், மயக்கும் ராகங்கள் (கட்டுரை)}}</ref> It is played in the event of war and other important events to communicate messages in the crowded place.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehindu.com/features/friday-review/music/secular-and-sacred/article4268995.ece|title=Secular and sacred|publisher=The Hindu|date=January 3, 2013|accessdate=September 10, 2016}}</ref>

