{{no footnotes|date=August 2018}} '''Suomen Naisyhdistys''' is a Finnish [[women's rights]] organisation. It was founded in 1884, and is the oldest women's movement organisation in [[Finland]]. It is a member of the [[International Alliance of Women]], that has [[general consultative status]] with the [[United Nations]].
